<div class="post-footer">May 6th, 2011 |  Category: <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/art/" title="View all posts in art" rel="category tag">art</a>, <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/copyleft/" title="View all posts in copyleft" rel="category tag">copyleft</a>, <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/free-culture/" title="View all posts in Free Culture" rel="category tag">Free Culture</a> | <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/2011/05/06/the-avatars-of-vishnu/#comments" class="comments-link"  title="Comment on The Avatars of Vishnu">78 comments</a> </div>
